  ]
}

### ============================================================================
### TEST 3 — Codebase error detected and reported (cache hit → fail → AuditEvent + error_report)
### ============================================================================
### No cache clearing needed — cache from tests 1+2 is reused.
###
### Flow (cache HIT):
###   lab-core POST → agent finds cached (create_exam, reflab) mapping
###   → send_direct injects ERR-LOINC + patient/practitioner into cached FHIR Bundle
###   → POST to reflab → 404 (LOINC code unknown in RefLab catalog)
###   → error_checker cross-references LabCore source code + integration docs
###   → diagnoses: ORIGIN_A (LabCore sends exam code not in RefLab's LOINC catalog)
###   → writes AuditEvent to IRIS FHIR (short outcomeDesc, no truncation)
###   → writes agent_error_report row (full evidence/suggestion/payload, no slicing)
###
### Simulated codebase bug:
###   LabCore's build_reflab_payload() sends exam_code as-is without validating
###   against reflab's LOINC catalog. When reflab doesn't recognize the code,
###   it returns 404. The error is in the codebase (LabCore) — not a contract
###   or infrastructure issue. It cannot be fixed immediately, but MUST be reported.
###
### Expected:
###   lab-core: 201 Created (SR itself is created successfully)
###   agent logs: cache_hit=True → sent → 404
###   agent logs: error_checker → origin=ORIGIN_A, confidence≈0.98
###   agent logs: FHIR AuditEvent created id=...
###   agent logs: error_report saved id=... audit_event_id=...
###
### Verify after ~15s:
###   docker compose logs agents --tail 10 | grep -E "(cache_hit|sent|AuditEvent|error_report)"
###   → cache_hit=True → sent → 404
###   → FHIR AuditEvent created id=...
###   → error_report saved id=... audit_event_id=...
### ============================================================================
POST http://localhost:8000/service-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "664d2678-29ce-450e-ab50-bd463364ded6",
  "practitioner_id": "35ca797f-5099-479d-91d5-fbe12a125b90",
  "priority": "ROUTINE",
  "notes": "Test 3 — codebase error, LOINC desconhecido no RefLab",
  "items": [
    { "exam_code": "ERR-LOINC", "exam_name": "Teste LOINC desconhecido (simulador)" }
  ]
}
